# Override the base URL used in copied play prompts and DESIGN.md quick-start instructions.
#
# Option 1 — automatic tunnel (recommended for local play testing):
#   npm run dev:tunnel
#   Starts ngrok + next dev together; NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL is set automatically.
#   Requires ngrok: https://ngrok.com/download
#
# Option 2 — set manually:
#   Uncomment and set to a tunnel URL, then restart the dev server.
#
# On Vercel: set to your canonical domain to prevent preview-deployment URLs
# appearing in copied prompts (e.g. https://sistema-bay-seven.vercel.app).
#
# Unset: falls back to window.location.origin at copy time (localhost URLs,
# not reachable by remote agents).

# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://your-tunnel-url.ngrok.io

# PostHog — product analytics
# Get these from posthog.com → your project → Project Settings → Project API Key
# NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_KEY=phc_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
# NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_HOST=https://us.i.posthog.com
